    "data": [
        {
            "title": "上然2期截收8380票 超額認購約64倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"上然2期截收8380票，超額認購約64倍。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c003dbf338e90a286799694aa8785710/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820535270598.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">上然2期截收8380票，超額認購約64倍。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>萬科香港旗下大埔馬窩路19號上然2期今日截票，共收8,380票，按明天以價單形式發售128伙計，暫錄超額認購約64倍。\n\n</p>\n<p>發展商從現有2張價單共206伙中挑選出128伙單位於明日開售，涉及12伙開放式、47伙1房、51伙2房、14伙3房及4伙特色戶。\n\n</p>\n<p>該批單位面積246至723方呎，價單定價318萬至1,179.2萬元，價單呎價11,793元至17,654元。以達16%的折扣優惠計算，折實售價267.2萬至990.6萬元，折實呎價9,907至14,830元，折實平均呎價11,863元，其中56伙折實售價低於400萬元，可受惠100元印花稅新措施。\n\n</p>\n<p>根據銷售安排，銷售當日分為A、B兩組，A組屬大手客組別，買家須購買2至8伙，最優先的A1組買家須選購指定3房或項目1期的4房單位，B組則為一般買家時段。<br/>\n \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060840/即時-地產-上然2期截收8380票-超額認購約64倍",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 21:01:22",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "亞姐練樂儀自認渣男磁石︰數量有一隻手  許嘉浩為女性朋友做媒人先觀察男方酒品",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c07f597f2840065fb1dbad8c0f25da8d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820242514790.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>由許嘉浩擔任主持的婚嫁喜宴配對平台，今日（28日）請來亞姐練樂儀做嘉賓，並以一身婚嫁晚裝亮相。自認不恨嫁的練樂儀，笑言挑選對象不能急，遇過渣男她說︰「我都有渣男磁石稱號，唔係好多，一隻手數得晒。」\n\n</p>\n<p>許嘉浩練樂儀\n\n</p>\n<p>談到擇偶條件，練樂儀說︰「要有責任心同對我好，仲要錫屋企人，呢啲好基本。最緊要適合，因為婚姻係兩個人嘅事，成世㗎嘛！」當笑問男士可需買袋給她，她笑言自己買便可。做過護士工作的練樂儀，表示未同過醫生拍拖，因為工作太忙，難有機會進一步了解。在旁的許嘉浩笑言有親友做醫生，身邊好多醫生朋友，可以介紹給練樂儀認識。許嘉浩又指樂做媒人為男女配對，成功配對過幾百人，也曾為練樂儀介紹對象，並笑稱收媒人利是都不錯。談到幾時再為練樂儀介紹對象？他笑言有，又指事前有約男方飲酒，從而觀察對方的酒品，從而得知那位男士並不適合練樂儀。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164356/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許嘉浩（右）擔任主持的婚嫁喜宴配對平台，找來亞姐練樂儀（左）擔任嘉賓。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/755a7b388d2d61a2a820528199f83ecd/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_34_14.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許嘉浩（右）擔任主持的婚嫁喜宴配對平台，找來亞姐練樂儀（左）擔任嘉賓。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164357/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"練樂儀穿上婚紗，唔急搵情人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cc2bd285603e1777ee97635b5e69430d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_34_15_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        練樂儀穿上婚紗，唔急搵情人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164363/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"去年許嘉浩（右）、林寶玉（左）、郭秀雲（中）一同擔任床具新店開幕嘉賓。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b70d3452b446fa2933e73b7904651179/2025-03/20241219_130352.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        去年許嘉浩（右）、林寶玉（左）、郭秀雲（中）一同擔任床具新店開幕嘉賓。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164364/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"練樂儀是2020亞洲小姐，她與許嘉浩老友鬼鬼，曾一同出席醫學美容店活動。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6f2a8676bcb43dc9a05747adf6073464/2025-03/DSY_2218.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        練樂儀是2020亞洲小姐，她與許嘉浩老友鬼鬼，曾一同出席醫學美容店活動。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164365/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許嘉浩早年擔任TVB真人騷《求愛大作戰》導師，穿透視紗裙上陣，有「綠魔」之稱。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/919bb9f6fc8d5613a646659c32375202/2025-03/IMG_5396.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許嘉浩早年擔任TVB真人騷《求愛大作戰》導師，穿透視紗裙上陣，有「綠魔」之稱。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164358/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"練樂儀做過護士，話工種繁複，好難有時間識醫生。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5bb91e4adce225e07a1d7a1f71ceb8c5/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_34_15_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        練樂儀做過護士，話工種繁複，好難有時間識醫生。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164359/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許嘉浩話不時介紹異性畀練樂儀認識。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/79ef6a25ace378e8b8fc9e02905faa8d/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_34_15.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許嘉浩話不時介紹異性畀練樂儀認識。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164361/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"許嘉浩表示身邊有唔少醫生朋友，練樂儀不妨埋嚟睇埋嚟揀。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1b4727f1475710562ff6f595d758b24/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-28_at_17_36_18_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        許嘉浩表示身邊有唔少醫生朋友，練樂儀不妨埋嚟睇埋嚟揀。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
