            "title": "七人欖球賽2025｜港女隊首戰擊敗哈薩克 「達陣王」莊嘉欣面向南看台達陣最開心",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"港女隊首戰擊敗哈薩克，「達陣王」莊嘉欣面向南看台達陣最開心。徐嘉華、劉駿軒攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/26298839728e846b33837ac51a9f7977/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820452171604.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">港女隊首戰擊敗哈薩克，「達陣王」莊嘉欣面向南看台達陣最開心。徐嘉華、劉駿軒攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>香港國際七人欖球賽除了舉行系列賽外，還有附屬的「Melrose銀劍賽」，港男、女隊在傍晚分途出擊，一起旗開得勝。香港女子隊在「達陣王」莊嘉欣2次達陣下，以29:14擊敗哈薩克，後者更完成目標面對南看台達陣，她矢言很開心，更形容出場時感覺似演唱會。\n\n</p><h2>「達陣王」莊嘉欣2次達陣</h2>\n<p>香港女子隊在「Melrose銀劍賽」首仗對哈薩克，憑「達陣王」莊嘉欣2次成功達陣下贏29:14。當選今場最佳球員的莊嘉欣表示，對着南看台達陣感覺最開心：「感覺很熟悉，側邊很嘈吵、很熱鬧，但在達陣一刻又很安靜，大家都期待我入波的感覺真的很好。」她說自己在達陣一刻嘗試享受觀眾的打氣聲。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"不少球迷支持港隊。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3029d2dd47686167715ed6ab8623ef4c/2025-03/2__22.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少球迷支持港隊。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"不少球迷支持港隊。劉駿軒攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a936cf17ccc95bb939d14c189b1cbea/2025-03/174316558789256.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        不少球迷支持港隊。劉駿軒攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港女子隊奮勇阻攔哈薩克隊。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0edbfabc9851bd2d8b1b3fa4cadf604b/2025-03/174316558725254.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港女子隊奮勇阻攔哈薩克隊。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"莊嘉欣率先為港隊達陣。徐嘉華攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/12989a1170d7aab05b34152794abc605/2025-03/2__4.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        莊嘉欣率先為港隊達陣。徐嘉華攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"莊嘉欣率先為港隊達陣。徐嘉華攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4e4315ecab1cfe0ef9ffbdb091d69661/2025-03/174316558786954.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        莊嘉欣率先為港隊達陣。徐嘉華攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31581fe8db854b84d88301747059ac6a/2025-03/2__0_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e917339aa335df2f8d7e2337cb29644/2025-03/3__3.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e820341f45b7466143d853ffbaa87e5a/2025-03/174316558795007.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊旗開得勝，擊敗哈薩克。徐嘉華攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>出場感覺似演唱會</h2>\n<p>今次是香港七欖首度移師啟德主場館，在新場地作賽，她感覺煥然一新，但氣氛依舊熱烈：「大球場感覺是老地方，是熟悉的七欖，今日則感覺煥然一新，場地不同，但觀眾熱烈的打氣程度依舊。」因為燈光和煙霧，她形容賽前從球員通道跑出來感覺似演唱會，而今天因激光投影表演而關了天幕讓打氣聲更大聲，她亦期待明天打開天幕會有新的感受。\n\n</p><h2>港女隊明午對泰國</h2>\n<p>對於今場比賽，這位賽後最佳球員給自己7至8分：「開頭我們可能因為緊張，被對手先入波，但之後我們慢慢打回自己的節奏。我覺得自己可以多些接應隊友的突破，當他們跑出時如何加快節奏，防守如何給予對手更大壓力。而剩下2、3分就看明天可否打出超水準。」香港女子隊明天中午將會對泰國。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fb93ca21b6ae4d7475cc774453df6a51/2025-03/2__23.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c96dd2a4116941553e76c6c664a4bce/2025-03/3__17.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/885310935374e789461945c5efb7ce53/2025-03/4__7.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f1729614a143ecb0877c121a827bfe5/2025-03/5__9.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/754d75e23fe8656e32581f960c55fb6e/2025-03/174316566516802.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        港女子隊擊敗哈薩克。劉駿軒攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
