        {
            "title": "天眼直擊｜粉嶺婦拾遺不報 一腳踩住地下銀包再放入袋 涉盜竊被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/2c357d1a744fdbe87c3a924138b819b6/2025-03/lo_0.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/20a276d80bcd71f09e894177d1c10102/192d8af349de4e40bc0220fccf9d1a37-0c939c72485e9381187fd5799ad5dec3-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e692c0d07cf\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67e692c0d07d1\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"天眼直擊｜粉嶺婦拾遺不報 一腳踩住地下銀包再放入袋 涉盜竊被捕 \" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1340e5f62ed935ec6dc3462d7af1c303/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820131276369.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">天眼直擊｜粉嶺婦拾遺不報 一腳踩住地下銀包再放入袋 涉盜竊被捕 </figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>上水分區昨日（3月27日）接獲一名女子報案，指其在3月26日於粉嶺聯和墟聯安街遺失一個銀包，懷疑被人盜去。上水分區特遣隊人員經深入調查後，今日（3月28日）粉嶺聯昌街以涉嫌「盜竊」拘捕一名70歲本地婦人，起回報案人被盗去失物。案件由大埔警區刑事調查隊第十隊跟進。\n\n</p>\n<p>早前失主曾在社區FB群組，上載附近麵包店的閉路電視片段追緝賊人。片段可見，當時銀包跌在了麵包店門口，然後涉案婦人行至，「踩住我個銀包，之後再拎起放入自己個袋度」，未幾便折返，全程僅約15秒。失主形容，婦人行徑是「鬼鬼鼠鼠」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164384/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"婦人行至麵包店門外。FB：北區之友\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aea5f952df6ddabd494ad3218186f75d/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-28-20h06m58s739.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        婦人行至麵包店門外。FB：北區之友\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164383/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"婦人一腳踩住地下銀包。FB：北區之友\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c45dc30626a52e9f2d1ef6c0e3c72b8f/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-28-20h07m03s807.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        婦人一腳踩住地下銀包。FB：北區之友\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164382/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"雖然不少街坊進出麵包店，但未有留意到老婦。FB：北區之友\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/607fd3f057baf069eb84f042aa09f32e/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-28-20h07m15s376.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雖然不少街坊進出麵包店，但未有留意到老婦。FB：北區之友\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164381/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"老婦附身拾起銀包。FB：北區之友\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7312e89ee3bfe73df94df95478dda23c/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-28-20h07m21s293.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        老婦附身拾起銀包。FB：北區之友\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164380/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"婦人得手後便徑自離去。FB：北區之友\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2aad791c2301a0e259bc59ac3b2f815e/2025-03/vlcsnap-2025-03-28-20h07m26s526.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        婦人得手後便徑自離去。FB：北區之友\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>警方重申，盜竊屬嚴重罪行，根據香港法例第210章《盜竊罪條例》第9條，一經定罪，最高可被判監禁十年。警方呼籲市民要小心保護財物，如發現任何可疑人或情況，應立即通知警方。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060834/即時-港聞-天眼直擊-粉嶺婦拾遺不報-一腳踩住地下銀包再放入袋-涉盜竊被捕",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 20:16:30",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "央行：兩人編造減息謠言被依法查處",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"中國人民銀行。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/45e39ecd571c1c20bbdbec40a6998077/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820055333497.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">中國人民銀行。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近期內地股市再度暢旺，許多敏感消息足以引發股市大升大跌。中國人民銀行今日發出通報，指內地兩名網民為搏流量，在網上騙造央行將減息的謠言，涉嫌擾亂金融秩序，被警方依法查處。\n\n</p>\n<p>通報稱，近期互聯網上傳播一則有關減息的虛假不實信息引發關注。中國人民銀行會同公安機關網安部門，依法打擊整治惡意編造涉金融領域網絡謠言違法行為。\n\n</p>\n<p>經查，黃某某（女，39歲）、聶某某（男，42歲）為博取關注、吸粉引流，假借財經媒體和信息服務機構名義發布降息謠言，誤導公眾認知，涉嫌擾亂金融秩序。目前，相關人員已被屬地公安機關依法查處。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060833/即時-中國-央行-兩人編造減息謠言被依法查處",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 20:11:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國網紅「甲亢哥」開啟中國行 京滬直播6小時",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f626ff62c5d7d0674ff630d96b7b8f77/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032820041463675.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>美國網紅「甲亢哥」近日首次開啟中國行，他連續在京滬等地開啟6小時直播，吸引全球數百萬網友觀看。鏡頭中他坐中國高鐵、參觀故宮長城、試駕小米電車，中國駐美大使館評論稱，數碼世界具影響力人士正彌合文化差距。\n\n</p><h2>中國使館：數碼世界正彌合文化差距</h2>\n<p>「甲亢哥」IShowSpeed甲亢哥原名小達倫·沃特金斯（Darren Watkins Jr.），在YouTube擁有3720萬粉絲，因其風格誇張，如得了「甲亢」，被中國網民稱為「甲亢哥」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3420627/TikTok%E9%9B%A3%E6%B0%91%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%B9%A7%E5%85%A5%E5%B0%8F%E7%B4%85%E6%9B%B8-%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%91%97%E6%80%A5%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%81%E7%A6%81\">TikTok難民｜美國網民湧入小紅書  有人著急：威脅更大要「禁」</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥和中國大媽互動。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cbe74fa626b64b025bd54edd270dda2f/2025-03/0328033.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥和中國大媽互動。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6da3fa0653c1b697a8d5a48e037af863/2025-03/0328035.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6238916df41aaf43d0c98b258757ee74/2025-03/0328036.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9c1719a1177fb40a3d34dac573fe7709/2025-03/0328037.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e4c40f6aee1a14119e7381750aa863da/2025-03/0328038.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ef28b19e4937db6e148de1074492e959/2025-03/0328040.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        甲亢哥在中國。 直播畫面\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>3月24日「甲亢哥」來到上海，到人民公園相親角與幾位大媽聊天，與歌手王嘉爾進行乒乓球對決，還看了舞獅、少林功夫和川劇變臉。夜遊外灘時，他驚歎「第一次見到這麼美的城市」。\n\n</p>\n<p>3月26日他轉戰北京，參觀故宮和長城，試穿老北京布鞋，還品嘗了豆汁、爆肚等特色美食。次日他首次乘坐了中國高鐵，網友們發現即使列車在隧道中行駛，直播也沒有出現卡頓。據悉未來長達半個月的旅程中，他還將去西安看兵馬俑，去成都看大熊貓。\n\n</p>\n<p>中國駐華盛頓大使館周三（26日）在社交平台X發文稱，「甲亢哥」之行表明在數碼世界具有影響力人士正在彌合文化差距，為外國觀眾了解充滿活力的中國創造新渠道。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2060832/即時-中國-美國網紅-甲亢哥-開啟中國行-京滬直播6小時",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-28 20:11:14",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "七人欖球賽2025︱啟德零售館人流略增 冀周末球迷更多帶動生意",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"七人欖球賽2025︱啟德零售館人流略增 冀周末球迷更多帶動生意\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/57deb378fdbd49e0591c8e2942545033/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032819511677178.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">七人欖球賽2025︱啟德零售館人流略增 冀周末球迷更多帶動生意</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>今日（28日）是香港國際七人欖球賽首日。《星島頭條》記者傍晚6時左右到鄰近啟德體育園的啟德零售館觀察，商場內人流不多，食肆未見排長龍情況。有運動品店售賣印有香港地名的欖球。\n\n</p>\n<p>美食廣場經理林先生表示，今日下午整體人流一般，中午時分外國人和學生比平時增加少許，推測因為今日是上班時間，期待周末兩日人流增多。他又表示，商戶需要配合商場安排，比賽期間暫時不會考慮延長營業時間，又指啟德體育園是香港的新園區和地標，認為舉辦更多類似的國際比賽對生意會有幫助。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164347/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"美食廣場經理林先生。汪旭峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/54f2cb1985c42283919fdfcb6f6127dc/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250328_192749390.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        美食廣場經理林先生。汪旭峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164352/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"未見食肆有排長龍的情況。汪旭峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ba87ffc3b35837e7149face5a1a70ff2/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250328_185647672_05.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        未見食肆有排長龍的情況。汪旭峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164353/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"未見食肆有排長龍的情況。汪旭峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ef2dd3e2f24ea81ec2f21ba9289a491/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250328_185647672_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        未見食肆有排長龍的情況。汪旭峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164354/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"商場內人流不多。汪旭峰攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3edc73dd7747a4960f3c3ca6c0bc9cf6/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250328_185647672_06.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        商場內人流不多。汪旭峰攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164355/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img al