            "title": "葵涌單位陷火海 疑電池短路肇禍 住戶吸入濃煙不適送院",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"葵涌單位陷火海 疑電池短路肇禍 住戶吸入濃煙不適送院\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bbbc5b7b91cc236b987d2b625998e707/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250328/_2025032819361668812.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">葵涌單位陷火海 疑電池短路肇禍 住戶吸入濃煙不適送院</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>葵涌石籬大隴街53至73號大廈一單位，今日（3月28日）下午4時許起火。網上圖片所見，單位火勢猛烈，濃煙衝天。消防接報趕至將火救熄，初步調查，相信上址一睡房有電池懷疑電線短路引致火警。\n\n</p>\n<p>事件中一名68歲姓何男住戶懷疑吸入濃煙不適，清醒被送往瑪嘉烈醫院治理，另有約60名居民自行疏散到安全位置。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164343/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"起火單位火光熊熊，濃煙衝天。FB：我們都是石籬邨長大的\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e317a817ab22f6c963a4b8aee5b2dce5/2025-03/videoframe_28433.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        起火單位火光熊熊，濃煙衝天。FB：我們都是石籬邨長大的\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4164342/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50d318efd19ef38710f516f816f6a13c/2025-03/videoframe_6743.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>